title: The Road To Heaven
summary: The Road To Heaven Adapted from the novel of the same name by the net literary god innocent. Wei Suo, a low-level small casual cultivator in Lingyue City, was unfortunately deceived during a transaction and obtained a broken low-level magic weapon. But in this broken magic weapon that is worthless, there is a spirit that has lived for tens of thousands of years. As a blessing in disguise, Wei Suo’s adventure journey begins… Road to Heaven Tongtian Zhi Luu Tōngtiān zhī Lù 通天之路
